<h2>‚ùó Common Reasons Transactions Get Stuck</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Network congestion or low fees</li>
    <li>Wrong address type (Legacy vs SegWit)</li>
    <li>Change addresses hiding balances until sync completes</li>
    <li>Typos in the receive address</li>
    <li>Wallet app outdated or temporarily glitching</li>
</ul>

