<h2>‚ùì FAQ</h2>
<details>
<summary>Click to expand FAQ</summary>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Q: Why is Mycelium Wallet showing zero balance?</strong><br>
        A: Usually due to HD account indexing or incomplete sync. Add indexes 1‚Äì3 and wait.</li>
    <li><strong>Q: Are my funds gone?</strong><br>
        A: No. With your correct seed (and passphrase), your coins are still on the blockchain.</li>
    <li><strong>Q: Can I recover with another wallet?</strong><br>
